race.description: Geoff Richards Panel Beating Mdn Hcp
race.comment: NUCLEAIRE (3) showed good early toe here two back when not beaten far in sixth in a strong maiden, then backed it up with another bold effort at Armidale when collared late. Peaking now and clearly the one to beat. CAPSITY (6) was midfield when resuming at Muswellbrook and was well supported. Blinkers go on and improvement is expected. TORENDOSETTA (4) ran a better race last start, finishing fourth at Muswellbrook. Peaking now and ready to fire. I'M OPINIONATED (9) struggles to break through but ended last prep with minor placings. Drawn to get a soft run and has winning claims on best figures.
